node.text: their pork bun is so delicious 😍

havent had tim ho wan in too long 😭 missed the bbq pork bun so much!! we had the beancurd skin, pork rib with yam and black bean, congee, carrot cake, chee cheong fan, fried taro and chicken dumplings (my fav) and hot and spicy wantonss
No other place does bbq pork bun as good as timhowan🤤

omg i love their char siew bun and the malay cake 🤤
Their bbq pork bun is the best!🤩
